cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about action recognition in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a generator network to improve the representation of motion vectors, which is a task related to machine learning (cs.MM), and the generator network is trained using a generative adversarial loss, which is a common technique in deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper uses the downstream action classification task to train the generator network, which is a task related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
